## Evaluation Matrix Templates

### Template 1: Problem Angle Comparison

Use when comparing different ways to frame or approach a problem.

```markdown
## Problem Angle Evaluation

| Criteria                     | Weight | Angle A | Angle B | Angle C |
| ---------------------------- | ------ | ------- | ------- | ------- |
| Addresses root cause         | 25%    | /10     | /10     | /10     |
| User can articulate problem  | 20%    | /10     | /10     | /10     |
| Differentiation potential    | 20%    | /10     | /10     | /10     |
| Market size at this angle    | 15%    | /10     | /10     | /10     |
| Team expertise alignment     | 10%    | /10     | /10     | /10     |
| Validation feasibility       | 10%    | /10     | /10     | /10     |
| **Weighted Total**           | 100%   |         |         |         |
```

